    "description": "<strong>Sanity Bunker</strong> plunges you into a terrifying survival experience deep within a desolate underground bunker. As the sole remaining technician, your mission is to keep the facility running—repair the failing pipes, revive the faltering generator, and ensure the systems don’t collapse. But you’re not alone. Something sinister haunts the bunker’s dark, suffocating corridors, a malevolent force from a forgotten past. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180480/extras/9118619887eb57887eb9910ccc23860d.avif?t=1728540683\" width=462 height=174 /></span><br><br>Every step you take is a test of your sanity, as you teeter on the edge of madness and survival. Can you endure the nightmare and unearth the horrifying secrets buried within the bunker before it’s too late?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180480/extras/57e2b332b73da2885d13c7b87713f3f6.avif?t=1728540683\" width=462 height=174 /></span>",
